00:00:37.320 --> 00:00:38.560
I told you

00:00:38.560 --> 00:00:40.159
not to trust humans.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:42.479
Especially that woman.

00:00:42.679 --> 00:00:44.280
But you refused to listen.

00:00:44.280 --> 00:00:45.799
Look where it's gotten you now.

00:00:47.479 --> 00:00:48.719
You've seen it yourself.

00:00:49.159 --> 00:00:50.600
She swore she'd always love you

00:00:50.600 --> 00:00:52.719
not long ago.

00:00:53.079 --> 00:00:55.679
And now she wants
to kill you, Li Motong.

00:00:56.079 --> 00:00:57.719
If you came just to mock me,

00:00:59.000 --> 00:00:59.799
get out.

00:01:00.719 --> 00:01:01.799
The gun is yours.

00:01:02.719 --> 00:01:04.319
And it's pointed at you now.

00:01:04.599 --> 00:01:05.719
Come to your senses,

00:01:06.120 --> 00:01:07.000
Li Motong.

00:01:08.560 --> 00:01:09.359
Get out!

00:01:10.719 --> 00:01:12.200
You're as stubborn as ever.

00:01:12.280 --> 00:01:13.200
Would you rather die

00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:14.560
for a woman who tried to kill you

00:01:14.560 --> 00:01:15.920
instead of taking back the Mei pearl?

00:01:15.920 --> 00:01:17.519
I'll protect her with my life.

00:01:18.480 --> 00:01:20.000
I won't let her be harmed.

00:01:23.480 --> 00:01:24.280
Fine.

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:26.680
Do you think I'll spare you

00:01:27.400 --> 00:01:28.879
just because
you refuse to take the pearl?

00:01:29.719 --> 00:01:31.560
Just wait and see.

00:02:07.519 --> 00:02:09.159
The Mei pearl belongs to Wujian.

00:02:09.759 --> 00:02:11.159
So why do you still hesitate

00:02:11.520 --> 00:02:13.360
to reclaim it?

00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:16.400
I accept whatever fate
my love for her brings.

00:02:16.800 --> 00:02:18.520
But why must you all

00:02:18.919 --> 00:02:20.360
keep standing in my way?

00:02:22.900 --> 00:02:23.879
Because the burden you carry

00:02:24.520 --> 00:02:26.080
is not yours alone.

00:02:26.280 --> 00:02:27.719
It concerns the fate of Wujian.

00:02:34.520 --> 00:02:36.000
Wujian cannot do without you.

00:02:36.319 --> 00:02:38.319
The choice is cruel.

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:39.800
Yet

00:02:40.639 --> 00:02:42.560
I must sacrifice that human.

00:02:42.960 --> 00:02:43.879
To me,

00:02:44.759 --> 00:02:45.879
she's not just anyone.

00:02:46.319 --> 00:02:48.080
She means more than my life.

00:02:49.159 --> 00:02:50.159
I can't sacrifice her

00:02:50.960 --> 00:02:52.199
just to save my own skin.

00:02:52.879 --> 00:02:54.919
But she knows the truth now.

00:02:55.879 --> 00:02:57.199
She'll never forgive you

00:02:57.479 --> 00:02:58.719
nor love you again.

00:03:01.159 --> 00:03:02.120
No matter what,

00:03:03.520 --> 00:03:05.199
it's time you let her go.

00:03:07.680 --> 00:03:08.919
I'm warning you.

00:03:09.879 --> 00:03:11.400
Don't stand in my way.

00:03:12.319 --> 00:03:14.120
And leave her alone.

00:03:40.199 --> 00:03:41.000
(Sister.)

00:03:42.319 --> 00:03:44.520
(It's over between him and me.)

00:03:46.360 --> 00:03:47.960
(What's left between us)

00:03:48.960 --> 00:03:50.439
(is only hatred.)

00:03:56.400 --> 00:03:57.520
They've been lenient with you,

00:03:57.520 --> 00:03:59.120
