00:03:59.800 --> 00:04:02.400
Killing you would be
as easy as crushing an ant.

00:04:02.560 --> 00:04:04.039
Go ahead and kill me, then.

00:04:04.439 --> 00:04:07.240
Why? Are you afraid
of thunder punishment?

00:04:07.639 --> 00:04:09.159
