00:06:00.120 --> 00:06:00.920
How fun.

00:06:01.800 --> 00:06:02.959
It's truly fun.

00:06:03.319 --> 00:06:04.040
Wait for me, Huayan.

00:06:04.040 --> 00:06:05.160
